---

## 💬 Communication

- Slack: `#artpulse-dev`
- Weekly check-ins: Wednesdays at 2pm GMT
- Code Review: All PRs require 1 reviewer approval

---

## 🧼 Contribution Guidelines

- Branch naming: `feature/`, `fix/`, `hotfix/`
- Pull requests should:
  - Reference an issue
  - Include screenshots or test steps
  - Pass lint and test checks

---

## 🔚 Final Notes

- Run `npm install` after pulling new changes if JS/CSS changed.
- Review the Codex for modular features and architecture.
- Ask if you’re unsure — the team is here to help!
